```

### 3. Key Features to Implement

**Header Section:**
- Logo + "Maestro" title
- Search button with kbd shortcut display

**Content Section:**
- Projects group with "+" button to add project
- Project tree using SidebarMenu > SidebarMenuItem > SidebarMenuSub structure
- Each project expandable to show issues
- Active state highlighting for current project/issue

**Footer Section:**
- "New Idea" link
- "Solo Chat" link (primary styled)

### 4. Navigation Click Handler
```typescript
// Wrap links to close mobile sidebar on navigation
function NavLink({ href, children, ...props }) {
  const { setOpenMobile } = useSidebar();
  return (
    <Link 
      href={href} 
      onClick={() => setOpenMobile(false)}
      {...props}
    >
      {children}
    </Link>
  );
}
```

