- [ ] Computes displayPath correctly (~ notation)
- [ ] Computes displayName correctly (custom or derived)
- [ ] Detects missing projects (path doesn't exist)
- [ ] Sorts by addedAt descending
- [ ] Returns empty array when no projects (not error)
- [ ] Returns 500 on unexpected errors

